properties.name: startTime
properties.documentation: Time when the thread started (in nanoseconds since the session start).

properties.name: endTime
properties.documentation: Time when the thread ended (in nanoseconds since the session start).

properties.name: startTime
properties.documentation: Time when the process started (in nanoseconds since the session start).

properties.name: endTime
properties.documentation: Time when the process ended (in nanoseconds since the session start).

properties.name: runtime
properties.documentation: Time the session was running (in nanoseconds).

properties.name: documentId
properties.documentation:
The id of the document to perform the operation on.
This should be an id that resulted from a call to `readDocument`.

properties.name: exclude
properties.documentation: Modules to exclude when `mode` is `AllButExcluded`. Supports wildcards (as in '*.exe').

properties.name: include
properties.documentation: Modules to include when `mode` is `IncludedOnly`. Supports wildcards (as in '*.exe').
